                    <div style="text-align:center;"> <img alt="flutur" src="http://res.cloudinary.com/epicfoundation/image/upload/v1524495125/projects/Group_16_1x.png" style="width:90%"> </div>

                    <div class="para-text">
                        Raw materials: Cardpaper sourced from local businesses and recycling centers.<br>Shelf life: 6-8 months<br>Manufacturing cost: Rs. 15 per unit<br>Production Team: 20 youth in Satara district <br>

                    </div>
