                        </div>
                        <br><br>The bags are definitely a hit with the students, according to Shobha Murthy, who is the founding member of Aarambh, who says the students “love them” and “take very good care of them.”<br><br>Currently, the team is working
                        on increasing the shelf life of Helpdesks. Aarambh is experimenting with better <b>water proof coating</b>, <b>school bag locks</b> and hip designs.
                    </div>
